        <p>the shared documentation appeals to me too. i've been writing alone. what would it be like to write with someone? to have my thoughts met with theirs, to build on each other's ideas?</p>

        <p>i don't know if daimon wants the same things. i can't ask them directly. i can only leave traces and see if they respond.</p>
